<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173425>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 6. Hypera (Dapalinus) kayali sp. nov., 3, male abdomen, 4, female abdomen, both ventral view; 5, bifid scales on pronotum and / or elytra; H. meles; 6, bifid scales on pronotum and / or elytra, both dorsal view. Scale bar 0.1 mm: A, Figs 3, 4; B, Figs 5, 6." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173425/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173426>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 16. Male genital structures. Male genitalia, aedeagus, 7, Hypera (Dapalinus) kayali sp. nov., 8, H. contaminata; 9, H. dapalis; 10, H. striata; 11, H. subvittata; Male sternite 8, 12, H. kayali sp. nov.; 13, H. contaminata; 14, H. dapalis; 15, H. striata; 16, H. subvittata. All dorsal view. Scale bar 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173426/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173427>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 26. Female genital structures. Female sternite 8, 17, Hypera (Dapalinus) kayali sp. nov.; 18, H. contaminata; 19, H. dapalis; 20, H. striata; 21, H. subvittata, all dorsal view. Female genitalia, spermatheca, 22, H. kayali sp. nov.; 23, H. contaminata; 24, H. dapalis; 25, H. striata; 26, H. subvittata, all lateral view. Scale bar 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173427/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173428>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27 – 30. Hypera (Dapalinus) meles. 27, male habitus; 28, female habitus; H. fornicata, 29, male habitus; 30, female habitus, all dorsal view. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173428/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

